> [troopjs-log](https://github.com/troopjs/troopjs-log) module provides convenient logging methods on component with
> [JavaScript Console](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/console) compliant API, log messages are by
> default printed in browser console but can also be piped into custom appender.
